1 Class Reunion is a very underated comedy gem . It 's 1982 and the 1972 class of Lizzie Borden High return for there 10 year reunion , among them are the usual stereotypes , the hunk , babe , the fat guy & nerd etc , but the former students are in for a bumpy night , one of their classmates is Walter Baloer , the class wimp who was subject to a comedy prank by the rest of the class on graduation night and since then has been in a mental home , Walter escapes and now plans to avenge his humiliation,,,,<br /><br />Despite the dark premise , this is really just an excuse for lots of very funny gags & set pieces . To say too much more would spoil the film but if you enjoyed the Naked Gun & Airplane movies you 'll love this , & what other film offers a music cameo by Chuck Berry ? . A great comedy which deserves a wider audience .
